entries.title_d: We need you to deliver the scan data that you got on your patrol to one of our smugglers immediately, so that we can plan our next point of attack.
entries.title: Endor system: Deliver scan data to a Rebel Smuggler.
entries.split_quest_alert: Rebel Command: < One of our scout ships have found one of these new Imperial ships and we are moving in for the attack now! >
entries.quest_rendezvous2_d: Our nearest smuggler has agreed to meet you at these coordinates, waste no time in getting there.
entries.quest_location_d: Even though you're moving out of the area with heavy Imperial presence, chances are that they are on to you and will try to chase you down so be ready.
entries.quest_dock2_d: If the surrounding area is safe, quickly dock with our smuggler and transfer the scan files.
entries.hello_d: Hi pilot, I was told you needed a express delivery.
entries.found_loc_d: Move out of there quickly to this location pilot. We have arranged for a smuggler to meet you there.
entries.failed_destroyed: We lost contact with the smuggler! What happened up there pilot? Return to base immediately!
entries.docking_started_delivery: Initiating docking. Lets do this fast, I don't like this area.
entries.docking_complete_delivery: Alright, I'm taking this to a nearby command fleet. Take care out there!
entries.attack_stopped: Tactical Computer: < No more fighter vessels within sensor range. >
entries.attack_notify: Tactical Computer: < Incoming fighter vessels. Scans show weapons armed. >
entries.arrived_at_delivery: You are at the correct location, dock and transfer the data to our smuggler.
